#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.70:0.2"
msgid "7. Ekadhammapeyyālavagga "
msgstr "7. Abbreviated Texts on One Thing "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 70. Dutiyakalyāṇamittasutta → dutiyakalyāṇamittasuttaṃ (bj) | kalyāṇamittatā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn45.70:0.3"
msgid "70. Dutiyakalyāṇamittasutta "
msgstr "70. Good Friends (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn45.70:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.70:1.2"
msgid "“Ekadhammo, bhikkhave, bahūpakāro ariyassa aṭṭhaṅgikassa maggassa uppādāya. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, one thing helps give rise to the noble eightfold path. "

msgctxt "sn45.70:1.3"
msgid "Katamo ekadhammo? "
msgstr "What one thing? "

msgctxt "sn45.70:1.4"
msgid "Yadidaṃ—kalyāṇamittatā. "
msgstr "It’s good friendship. "

msgctxt "sn45.70:1.5"
msgid "Kalyāṇamittassetaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvessati, ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarissati. "
msgstr "A mendicant with good friends can expect to develop and cultivate the noble eightfold path. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.70:1.6"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kalyāṇamitto ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti, ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti? "
msgstr "And how does a mendicant with good friends develop and cultivate the noble eightfold path? "

msgctxt "sn45.70:1.7"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti rāgavinayapariyosānaṃ dosavinayapariyosānaṃ mohavinayapariyosānaṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti rāgavinayapariyosānaṃ dosavinayapariyosānaṃ mohavinayapariyosānaṃ. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion, which culminate in the removal of greed, hate, and delusion. "

msgctxt "sn45.70:1.8"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kalyāṇamitto ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti, ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarotī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant with good friends develops and cultivates the noble eightfold path.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.70:1.9"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

